ON,483,152,55,450,AudibleSansMd,32,255,255,255.jpg"},"subtitle":"A Full-Cast BBC Radio Dramatisation","thesaurus_subject_keywords":["la_confidential","dramatizations"],"title":"The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring"},{"asin":"B009ABIN72","asset_details":[],"authors":[{"asin":"B000ARC6KA","name":"J. R. R. Tolkien"}],"available_codecs":[{"enhanced_codec":"LC_64_22050_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_22_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_32_22050_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_22_32"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_64_44100_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_44_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_128_44100_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_44_128"},{"enhanced_codec":"aax","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":false,"name":"aax"}],"category_ladders":[{"ladder":[{"id":"18574426011","name":"Literature & Fiction"},{"id":"18574449011","name":"Classics"}],"root":"Genres"},{"ladder":[{"id":"18580606011","name":"Science Fiction & Fantasy"},{"id":"18580607011","name":"Fantasy"},{"id":"18580615011","name":"Epic"}],"root":"Genres"}],"content_delivery_type":"MultiPartBook","content_type":"Product","format_type":"unabridged","has_children":true,"is_adult_product":false,"is_listenable":true,"is_preview_enabled":false,"is_purchasability_suppressed":false,"is_vvab":false,"issue_date":"2012-10-09","language":"english","merchandising_summary":"The Return of the King is the towering climax to J. R. R. Tolkien’s trilogy that tells the saga of the hobbits of Middle-earth and the great War of the Rings. In this concluding volume, Frodo and Sam make a terrible journey to the heart of the Land of the Shadow in a final reckoning with the...","narrators":[{"name":"Rob Inglis"}],"product_images":{"1000":"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81bUWxgo53L._SL1000_.jpg"},"publication_datetime":"2012-10-09T05:00:00Z","publication_name":"The Lord of the Rings","publisher_name":"Recorded Books","publisher_summary":"<p><i>The Return of the King</i> is the towering climax to J. R. R. Tolkien’s trilogy that tells the saga of the hobbits of Middle-earth and the great War of the Rings. In this concluding volume, Frodo and Sam make a terrible journey to the heart of the Land of the Shadow in a final reckoning with the power of Sauron. </p> <p>In addition to narrating the prose passages, Rob Inglis sings the trilogy’s songs and poems a capella, using melodies composed by Inglis and Claudia Howard, the Recorded Books studio director. This recording also contains Tolkien’s preface to the trilogy, including a prior history of the ring, and shire habitat, history, and folkways.</p>","rating":{"num_reviews":727,"overall_distribution":{"average_rating":4.86554383978487,"display_average_rating":"4.9","display_stars":5.0,"num_five_star_ratings":25362,"num_four_star_ratings":2267,"num_one_star_ratings":84,"num_ratings":28262,"num_three_star_ratings":450,"num_two_star_ratings":99},"performance_distribution":{"average_rating":4.841577729984174,"display_average_rating":"4.8","display_stars":5.0,"num_five_star_ratings":21606,"num_four_star_ratings":2385,"num_one_star_ratings":58,"num_ratings":24643,"num_three_star_ratings":495,"num_two_star_ratings":99},"story_distribution":{"average_rating":4.88817013018517,"display_average_rating":"4.9","display_stars":5.0,"num_five_star_ratings":22587,"num_four_star_ratings":1664,"num_one_star_ratings":34,"num_ratings":24734,"num_three_star_ratings":381,"num_two_star_ratings":68}},"release_date":"2012-10-09","runtime_length_min":1099,"series":[{"asin":"B009CFOEGK","sequence":"3","title":"The Lord of the Rings","url":"/pd/The-Lord-of-the-Rings-Audiobook/B009CFOEGK"}],"sku":"BK_RECO_006157","sku_lite":"BK_RECO_006157","social_media_images":{"facebook":"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51khjD+sTyL._SL10_UR1600,800_CR200,50,1200,630_CLa%7C1200,630%7C51khjD+sTyL.jpg%7C0,0,1200,630+82,82,465,465_PJAdblSocialShare-Gradientoverlay-largeasin-0to70,TopLeft,0,0_PJAdblSocialShare-AudibleLogo-Large,TopLeft,600,270_OU01_ZBLISTENING%20ON,617,216,52,500,AudibleSansMd,30,255,255,255.jpg","ig_bg":"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51khjD+sTyL._SL200_BL80_UR1080,2160.jpg","ig_static_with_bg":"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51khjD+sTyL._SL200_BL80_UR1080,2160_CLa%7C1080,2160%7C51khjD+sTyL.jpg%7C0,0,1080,2160+288,614,500,500_PJAdblSocialShare-Gradientoverlay-Radial,TopLeft,0,0_PJAdblSocialShare-AudibleLogo-Small,TopLeft,290,461_ZBLISTENING%20ON,290,410,52,500,AudibleSansMd,34,255,255,255_ZBThe%20Return%20of%20the%20King,290,1183,52,500,AudibleSansSm,32,255,255,255_ZBJ.%20R.%20R.%20Tolkien,290,1247,52,500,AudibleSansRg,28,255,255,255.jpg","ig_sticker":"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71UyRin7-TL._CLa%7C614,913%7C51khjD+sTyL.jpg%7C0,0,614,913+70,79,471,473_FMpng_PJAudible-logo-dk,BottomLeft,70,-100_ZAThe%20Return%20of%20t...,70,560,65,500,AudibleSansSm,42,54,54,54_ZAby%20J.%20R.%20R.%20Tolkien,70,640,52,517,AudibleSansRg,32,0,0,0.png","twitter":"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51khjD+sTyL._SL10_UR1600,800_CR200,50,1024,512_CLa%7C1024,512%7C51khjD+sTyL.jpg%7C0,0,1024,512+67,67,376,376_PJAdblSocialShare-Gradientoverlay-twitter-largeasin-0to60,TopLeft,0,0_PJAdblSocialShare-AudibleLogo-Medium,TopLeft,490,223_OU01_ZBLISTENING%20ON,483,152,55,450,AudibleSansMd,32,255,255,255.jpg"},"subtitle":"Book Three in the Lord of the Rings Trilogy","thesaurus_subject_keywords":["la_confidential"],"title":"The Return of the King"},{"asin":"B0099RKI5W","asset_details":[],"authors":[{"asin":"B000ARC6KA","name":"J. R. R. Tolkien"}],"available_codecs":[{"enhanced_codec":"LC_128_44100_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_44_128"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_32_22050_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_22_32"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_64_22050_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_22_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_64_44100_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_44_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"aax","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":false,"name":"aax"}],"category_ladders":[{"ladder":[{"id":"18572091011","name":"Children's Audiobooks"},{"id":"18572491011","name":"Literature & Fiction"},{"id":"18572503011","name":"Classics"}],"root":"Genres"},{"ladder":[{"id":"18572091011","name":"Children's Audiobooks"},{"id":"18572586011","name":"Science Fiction & Fantasy"},{"id":"18572587011","name":"Fantasy & Magic"}],"root":"Genres"},{"ladder":[{"id":"18580715011","name":"Teen & Young Adult"},{"id":"18580894011","name":"Literature & Fiction"},{"id":"18580902011","name":"Classics"}],"root":"Genres"},{"ladder":[{"id":"18580715011","name":"Teen & Young Adult"},{"id":"18581048011","name":"Science Fiction & Fantasy"},{"id":"18581049011","name":"Fantasy"},{"id":"18581055011","name":"Epic"}],"root":"Genres"}],"content_delivery_type":"MultiPartBook","content_type":"Product","editorial_reviews":["<p>\"Rob Inglis expertly bridges the gap between the whimsical, childlike aspects of Tolkien's fantasy classic and the hints of darker things to come later in <i>The Lord of the Rings</i>. Though content to enjoy his cozy life, cheerful hobbit Mr. Bilbo Baggins agrees to help his wizard friend Gandalf aid a group of dwarves seeking their lost treasure. As their various adventures ensue, Inglis treats listeners to a tour-de-force performance rich in colorful characterizations and several engaging singing performances. This story should be the unquestionable starting point for those venturing into Tolkien’s Middle-earth. Listeners experience a vocal performance that is in turn charming, gripping, a little scary, and always engaging.\" (<i>AudioFile</i> magazine)</p>"],"format_type":"unabridged","has_children":true,"is_adult_product":false,"is_listenable":true,"is_preview_enabled":false,"is_purchasability_suppressed":false,"is_vvab":false,"issue_date":"2012-10-09","language":"english","merchandising_summary":"Like every other hobbit, Bilbo Baggins likes nothing better than a quiet evening in his snug hole in the ground, dining on a sumptuous dinner in front of a fire. But when a wandering wizard captivates him with tales of the unknown, Bilbo becomes restless. Soon he joins the wizard’s band of...","narrators":[{"name":"Rob Inglis"}],"product_images":{"1000":"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81K05vSpbxL._SL1000_.jpg"},"publication_datetime":"2012-10-09T05:00:00Z","publication_name":"The Lord of the Rings","publisher_name":"Recorded Books","publisher_summary":"<p>Like every other hobbit, Bilbo Baggins likes nothing better than a quiet evening in his snug hole in the ground, dining on a sumptuous dinner in front of a fire. But when a wandering wizard captivates him with tales of the unknown, Bilbo becomes restless. Soon he joins the wizard’s band of homeless dwarves in search of giant spiders, savage wolves, and other dangers. Bilbo quickly tires of the quest for adventure and longs for the security of his familiar home. But before he can return to his life of comfort, he must face the greatest threat of all—a treasure-troving dragon named Smaug.</p> <p>In this fantasy classic, master storyteller J.R.R. Tolkein creates a bewitching world filled with delightful creatures and thrilling dangers. Narrator Rob Inglis will hold listeners of all ages spellbound with his skillful portrayal of hobbits, dwarves, and enchanted beasts.</p>","rating":{"num_reviews":3210,"overall_distribution":{"average_rating":4.763733963336224,"display_average_rating":"4.8","display_stars":5.0,"num_five_star_ratings":55544,"num_four_star_ratings":8351,"num_one_star_ratings":499,"num_ratings":66878,"num_three_star_ratings":1998,"num_two_star_ratings":486},"performance_distribution":{"average_rating":4.728041881280081,"display_average_rating":"4.7","display_stars":4.5,"num_five_star_ratings":47644,"num_four_star_ratings":8387,"num_one_star_ratings":433,"num_ratings":59215,"num_three_star_ratings":2268,"num_two_star_ratings":483},"story_distribution":{"average_rating":4.796677001887301,"display_average_rating":"4.8","display_stars":5.0,"num_five_star_ratings":50649,"num_four_star_ratings":6318,"num_one_star_ratings":319,"num_ratings":59344,"num_three_star_ratings":1702,"num_two_star_ratings":356}},"release_date":"2012-10-09","runtime_length_min":665,"series":[{"asin":"B009CFOEGK","sequence":"0.5","title":"The Lord of the Rings","url":"/pd/The-Lord-of-the-Rings-Audiobook/B009CFOEGK"}],"sku":"BK_RECO_006155","sku_lite":"BK_RECO_006155","social_media_images":{"facebook":"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51U7W9O0UKL._SL10_UR1600,800_CR200,50,1200,630_CLa%7C1200,630%7C51U7W9O0UKL.jpg%7C0,0,1200,630+82,82,465,465_PJAdblSocialShare-Gradientoverlay-largeasin-0to70,TopLeft,0,0_PJAdblSocialShare-AudibleLogo-Large,TopLeft,600,270_OU01_ZBLISTENING%20ON,617,216,52,500,AudibleSansMd,30,255,255,255.jpg","ig_bg":"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51U7W9O0UKL._SL200_BL80_UR1080,2160.jpg","ig_static_with_bg":"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51U7W9O0UKL._SL200_BL80_UR1080,2160_CLa%7C1080,2160%7C51U7W9O0UKL.jpg%7C0,0,1080,2160+288,614,500,500_PJAdblSocialShare-Gradientoverlay-Radial,TopLeft,0,0_PJAdblSocialShare-AudibleLogo-Small,TopLeft,290,461_ZBLISTENING%20ON,290,410,52,500,AudibleSansMd,34,255,255,255_ZBThe%20Hobbit,290,1183,52,500,AudibleSansSm,32,255,255,255_ZBJ.%20R.%20R.%20Tolkien,290,1247,52,500,AudibleSansRg,28,255,255,255.jpg","ig_sticker":"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71UyRin7-TL._CLa%7C614,913%7C51U7W9O0UKL.jpg%7C0,0,614,913+70,79,471,473_FMpng_PJAudible-logo-dk,BottomLeft,70,-100_ZAThe%20Hobbit,70,560,65,500,AudibleSansSm,42,54,54,54_ZAby%20J.%20R.%20R.%20Tolkien,70,640,52,517,AudibleSansRg,32,0,0,0.png","twitter":"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51U7W9O0UKL._SL10_UR1600,800_CR200,50,1024,512_CLa%7C1024,512%7C51U7W9O0UKL.jpg%7C0,0,1024,512+67,67,376,376_PJAdblSocialShare-Gradientoverlay-twitter-largeasin-0to60,TopLeft,0,0_PJAdblSocialShare-AudibleLogo-Medium,TopLeft,490,223_OU01_ZBLISTENING%20ON,483,152,55,450,AudibleSansMd,32,255,255,255.jpg"},"thesaurus_subject_keywords":["la_confidential"],"title":"The Hobbit"},{"asin":"B009ABHTF4","asset_details":[],"authors":[{"asin":"B000ARC6KA","name":"J. R. R. Tolkien"}],"available_codecs":[{"enhanced_codec":"LC_64_44100_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_44_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_128_44100_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_44_128"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_64_22050_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_22_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_32_22050_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_22_32"},{"enhanced_codec":"aax","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":false,"name":"aax"}],"category_ladders":[{"ladder":[{"id":"18574426011","name":"Literature & Fiction"},{"id":"18574449011","name":"Classics"}],"root":"Genres"},{"ladder":[{"id":"18580606011","name":"Science Fiction & Fantasy"},{"id":"18580607011","name":"Fantasy"},{"id":"18580615011","name":"Epic"}],"root":"Genres"}],"content_delivery_type":"MultiPartBook","content_type":"Product","format_type":"unabridged","has_children":true,"is_adult_product":false,"is_listenable":true,"is_preview_enabled":false,"is_purchasability_suppressed":false,"is_vvab":false,"issue_date":"2012-10-09","language":"english","merchandising_summary":"The Two Towers is the second volume of J.R.R. Tolkien's epic saga, The Lord of the Rings. The Fellowship has been forced to split up. Frodo and Sam must continue alone towards Mount Doom, where the One Ring must be destroyed. Meanwhile, at Helm’s Deep and Isengard, the first great battles of...","narrators":[{"name":"Rob Inglis"}],"product_images":{"1000":"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81CgKCSTThL._SL1000_.jpg"},"publication_datetime":"2012-10-09T05:00:00Z","publication_name":"The Lord of the Rings","publisher_name":"Recorded Books","publisher_summary":"<p><i>The Two Towers</i> is the second volume of J.R.R. Tolkien's epic saga, <i>The Lord of the Rings</i>. </p> <p>The Fellowship has been forced to split up. Frodo and Sam must continue alone towards Mount Doom, where the One Ring must be destroyed. Meanwhile, at Helm’s Deep and Isengard, the first great battles of the War of the Ring take shape. </p> <p>In this splendid, unabridged audio production of Tolkien’s great work, all the inhabitants of a magical universe - hobbits, elves, and wizards - spring to life. Rob Inglis’ narration has been praised as a masterpiece of audio.</p>","rating":{"num_reviews":1168,"overall_distribution":{"average_rating":4.882946076282332,"display_average_rating":"4.9","display_stars":5.0,"num_five_star_ratings":45493,"num_four_star_ratings":3825,"num_one_star_ratings":98,"num_ratings":50182,"num_three_star_ratings":641,"num_two_star_ratings":125},"performance_distribution":{"average_rating":4.85171094101756,"display_average_rating":"4.9","display_stars":5.0,"num_five_star_ratings":39220,"num_four_star_ratings":4146,"num_one_star_ratings":97,"num_ratings":44420,"num_three_star_ratings":818,"num_two_star_ratings":139},"story_distribution":{"average_rating":4.896547067032818,"display_average_rating":"4.9","display_stars":5.0,"num_five_star_ratings":40748,"num_four_star_ratings":2972,"num_one_star_ratings":63,"num_ratings":44426,"num_three_star_ratings":557,"num_two_star_ratings":86}},"release_date":"2012-10-09","runtime_length_min":1000,"series":[{"asin":"B009CFOEGK","sequence":"2","title":"The Lord of the Rings","url":"/pd/The-Lord-of-the-Rings-Audiobook/B009CFOEGK"}],"sku":"BK_RECO_006158","sku_lite":"BK_RECO_006158","social_media_images":{"facebook":"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/517Ntsz3GqL._SL10_UR1600,800_CR200,50,1200,630_CLa%7C1200,630%7C517Ntsz3GqL.jpg%7C0,0,1200,630+82,82,465,465_PJAdblSocialShare-Gradientoverlay-largeasin-0to70,TopLeft,0,0_PJAdblSocialShare-AudibleLogo-Large,TopLeft,600,270_OU01_ZBLISTENING%20ON,617,216,52,500,AudibleSansMd,30,255,255,2